channel.title: Help with the client my server is running on
channel.description:
alright...well i just got a new laptop for my birthday and...
everytime i run silab or any other client at a random time (and short) it closes out of the client and sends me error report...
[code]# # A fatal error has been detected by the Java Runtime Environment: # # EXCEPTION_ACCESS_VIOLATION (0xc0000005) at pc=0x000000006d8418c6, pid=2840, t id=4956 # # JRE version: 6.0_14-b08 # Java VM: Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (14.0-b16 mixed mode windows-amd64 ) # Problematic frame: # V [jvm.dll+0x518c6] # # An error report file with more information is saved as: # C:\Users\Ashli Michelle\Desktop\Antares-FatalScape\hs_err_pid2840.log # # If you would like to submit a bug report, please visit: # http://java.sun.com/webapps/bugreport/crash.jsp # Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
help with this please?
